    "After a successful career in the museum world, he retired in 1959.": [],
    "He was still active and involved in many activities when he suddenly died, in 1961, at the age of 67.": [],
    "By that time, the rebuilding of the department of sculpture and applied arts in the western inner court of the museum was still in progress.": [],
    "This part of the renovation was realized in 1962, under his successor, <a href=\"/vanschendela\">Arthur F. \u00c9. Van Schendel</a>.</p>": []
